The paper focuses on facial expression translation, which is a task related to computer vision (cs.CV). The proposed method is based on a conditional GAN, which is a popular deep learning technique for image generation (cs.LG). The paper also discusses the use of a face mask loss to reduce the influence of background changing, which is a technique related to artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The proposed framework includes a module for facial expression recognition, which is a task related to multimedia (cs.MM) and human-computer interaction (cs.HC).
